snippet.title: Voidspire Tactics Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Available on Steam! 
http://store.steampowered.com/app/415920/

---

Voidspire Tactics is an indie turn-based Tactics RPG with a heavy emphasis on exploration, character progression, and highly tactical combat.
